Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被傳銷給...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還納悶你出去幹嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是被傳銷給套住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背著一屁股債回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像你的作風 佐藤前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個洗滌劑真的不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然成分100%
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和市面上的不同 完全不起沫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道嗎 去污要利用摩擦力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你們也去說明會聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會理解商品的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也會加盟的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣不斷拉人入伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤前輩也會升職
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種體系沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不叫傳銷叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳銷？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她也對你沒轍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那女孩做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間也是她收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經晚了 明天再去退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退貨這個...有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都買回來了再去退有點不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會給對方添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且說不定有人肯買呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想賣給誰？怎麼賣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了自己是個家裡蹲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡蹲怎麼可能出門做生意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這些都是為你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天記得去退貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為家裡蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再出門也是情理之中吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳銷一點都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不安...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 早上好佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話要說？今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就在那家店見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:06:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著這麼大的袋子 是誰都會發覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個被傳銷騙了的大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話就說出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都在暗笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的 該死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼倒霉的總是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 果然還是不還不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有其他選擇的餘地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你還僥倖認為有人肯買？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是覺得隨著時間流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商品和欠債都能自己消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你現在不罷手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還會有更多指標落到你頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時你的欠債也會越滾越大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎 佐藤前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 前輩一直都這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨Refrain 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起 已經有兩個合夥人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來Cleaning off的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Cooling-off
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}[注:根據合同規定期限 在一定期間內締約人具有撤回的權力]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說道具太貴?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道為了入手這些我費了多大勁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊玩去 白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 稍後我會把解約文件寄給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為會磨很久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 我們可是有正經理念的生意人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會像無賴公司那樣玩花招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為佐藤一定會成功的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然對家裡蹲來說有點勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤 平時三餐都好好吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...有時會漏掉一兩餐...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是吃快餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我是一個人住...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近雜誌上發表的論文指出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡蹲和飲食也有很大的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣寫的沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡蹲的最大原因在於飲食
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤認識英語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當...當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是吃快餐容易導致腦內物質缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思維消極遲鈍 最終導致家裡蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子你也是常吃快餐食品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時也會想窩在家裡不出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人際關係不如意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是和學校的朋友等人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是因為腦內物質缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是佐藤的女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通朋友也沒關係 你聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補充腦內物質的最好辦法是科學飲食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青菜要吃沒農藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉類也要挑沒喂添加劑的牲畜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調料要仔細斟酌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不顯眼的地方往往混有化學材料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有做料理的時候不推薦用煤氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的是用碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如備長炭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}[備長炭：優質木炭]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 以上方法都有缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼缺點？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費時間和金錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實還有更好的辦法...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:11:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你們聽到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這個是內部消息 要保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了班長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次算特例
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們爭取到了呢 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就能和家裡蹲說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到人世間竟然有這等好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是MouseLord的獨創配方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也是天然100%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生產過程中為了避免摻入化學物質
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們引入了最新的科學理念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天定量服用 會促進腦細胞活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思維積極向前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離家裡蹲也指日可待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真可惜 這些都是內部產品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然佐藤要撤約的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個不能零買
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要買就得買一套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套要多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續加盟不解約的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以8折優惠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8折？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤前輩不買的話我買
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要入伙就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等 我還沒解約呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒說過不買
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我一個人吃的話量有點多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多出來的賣給熟人不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 前提是那個人也要加盟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還有這一手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就通過佐藤前輩來買
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷拉人加盟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤也會有佣金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利的話不僅可以脫離家裡蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以獲得一大筆收入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這正是Japanese Dream！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了班長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠這個實現自己的遠大理想！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望真的能抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岬 這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說傳銷解約的時候麻煩很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了以防萬一我帶上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面都寫了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clean...不 Cooling-off時的注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出Cooling-off時 對方往往會一口答應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之後會花言巧語介紹別的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來別說Cooling-off了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會被騙買其它商品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定要留心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是Cooling-off卻被騙買其它商品？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上還真有這種傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是說我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能再去一次Cooling-off了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再用正攻法的話還會重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然懂 關鍵是不要被對方牽著鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貫徹自己的方針就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面都寫了 拿來參考如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下 能賞光做個調查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是黑川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是昨天加盟的佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林的家？我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和班長一起主持說明會的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說想Cooling-off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他便爽快地告訴了我班長的住址
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那樣子 他和班長是同等地位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想借此拖後對手的業績吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陽台獨立房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}[註：低層連續戶型 每戶都有獨立的陽台和庭院]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫陽台獨立房？你淨知道些奇怪的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叔叔是專門搞這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老同學來拜訪 你也太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼 我叫警察了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一而再再而三地騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你？你有證據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再胡說的話 我要告你誹謗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是來Cooling-off罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是你家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要找借口說解約文件不在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 旁邊有家餐館
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在那裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了文件就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可不吃這一手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想玩緩兵之計
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些還你 簽了字後我們就走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門讓我們進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多Mouselord的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想笑就笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們不同 已經沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論用什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把這些都賣光的話 我就沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面簽字 趕快走人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然跟你合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中時就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼在這種時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 只是我養的寵物在鬧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餵它點東西就老實了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寵物？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你養的是老虎還是獅子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別管 我就是為了養活它才進Mouselord的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說你們滿意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 你在幹什麼！快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個角色是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托羅托羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你的RMT能夠進展順利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是你能做到的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個人就是托羅托羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0)}{\pos(432,350)}第18話 黑暗的未來歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼一擲千金！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.45,0:23:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定有人能使之成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不如這樣死掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 歡迎邂逅青之鳥
